title: SEC Sues Elon Musk in San Francisco Federal Court to Enforce Subpoena
description: The agency sued Elon Musk over his failure to testify in an investigation of his Twitter takeover.

title: Are Fridge Magnets 'Lowbrow'? Appliance Manufacturers Have Decided: Yes
description: How fridge-magnet lovers are coping with an industry move away from magnetic materials. Plus three tips for anyone who refuses to give up the habit of slapping mementos on their coolers.

title: Americans Are Asking AI: 'Should I Get Back With My Ex?'
description: New apps like Rizz and YourMove are using advanced language models to help nervous romantics win the affection of potential partners. Others promise to tell you if the love of your life might be someone you’ve already met.

title: Bill Gates-Backed Startup Launches AI Chatbot for Personalized Entertainment Picks
description: The chatbot, called Pix, runs on OpenAI language-processing tech and will learn user preferences over time.
